high_descs: Hang a right at the wall and walk to the black chair ahead.
Pick up the newspaper from the cushion on the chair.
Turn right, hang a right at the fireplace and walk to the white side table next to the green chair on the left.
Turn on the small lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn to the right and walk to the chair.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Turn to the right and then make another right. Go straight to the side table with the lamp.
Use the newspaper to turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp with a newspaper.

high_descs: Move forward and then turn right. Face the dark chair in the corner.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Carry the newspaper and turn to the right. Then turn right again and left to find the small table beside the couch.
Hold the newspaper and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Hold a newspaper and turn on the lamp.
